  m_Name: Sm nar night
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NarrationLines
  lines:
  - Night time has fallen over the city.
  - 'The lights of buildings outside shimmering light stars. '
  - I walk up to the old bridge once again.
  - 'The moon illumniates the area as I approach it '
  - I feel the same ominous feeling...
  - She's here.
  - I just need to stay calm
